a moves to Texas and=C2=A0gives Musk a giant new pay package in 2025, a sha=
reholder sues, and a Texas court strikes it down. It=E2=80=99s also entirel=
y possible! The rules in Texas and Delaware are =E2=80=9Cessentially the sa=
me=E2=80=9D! Supposedly!=C2=A0Nonetheless, Tesla is asking its shareholders=
 to approve Musk=E2=80=99s pay again, now, while it=E2=80=99s still in Dela=
