=09Or, if you=C2=A0do=C2=A0sign an employment contract with the new bank be=
fore shopping their offer to your old bank, make sure that the employment c=
ontract does not contain a non-negotiable =E2=80=9Cbreakup fee=E2=80=9D req=
uiring you to pay back $4 million to the new bank if you don=E2=80=99t end =
up working there.=09Or, if you=C2=A0do=C2=A0sign an employment contract wit=
h the new bank before shopping their offer to your old bank, and if the emp=
loyment contract=C2=A0does=C2=A0contain a $4 million breakup fee, and if yo=
u shop the offer to your old bank, and they want to keep you and make a goo=
