al with your old bank, there=E2=80=99s a provision saying =E2=80=9Cif New B=
ank sues me to enforce that breakup fee, Old Bank will pay for my lawyers, =
and if New Bank wins that lawsuit, Old Bank will pay the $4 million.=E2=80=
