ottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">=
20.5% of the stock</a>, but the judge found in January that he is a control=
ling shareholder through his share ownership, =E2=80=9Csuperstar CEO=E2=80=
=9D status and dominance of the board. Or technically she found that he was=
 a controlling shareholder in 2017, but I think the analysis is pretty much=
