</div>
<div id=3D"footnote-6" class=3D"footnote-content" style=3D"font-style: ital=
ic;">
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">[6] The judge, carefully, wrote that Tesla "fa=
iled to prove that the Grant was the product of fair dealing or at a fair p=
rice," not that it *was* unfair; there is room for the outcome to change if=
